{"tid":984454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"捧三房超蓮場 猷君收蛋糕慶祝生日：Thanks 細家姐！","createTime":"2019-01-16T21:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T09:57:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db846ab353068522b1f37c12024dc51f2f5420c7","tid":984454,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T21:14:25.000Z","msg":"賭王何鴻燊四房子女各有發展，平日交流似乎唔多，不過，邊個話同父異母就冇friend做？今晚四房細仔猷君去咗三房家姐超蓮間麵店，試過家姐間舖啲出品，猷君以英語留言話自己終於都去到，啱啱喺今個月12號度過24歲生日嘅佢仲獲贈迷你生日蛋糕，不過猷君爆原來此蛋糕僅屬家姐「私人醒」，只得佢先有咁話。<br />\n而猷君當然不忘要幫家姐賣吓廣告，大讚啲豬腸同紅腸好食，最後更不忘致謝：「Thanks 细家姐！」<br />\n至於超蓮，雖然冇po同細佬嘅相，但就轉發咗早前同佢一齊去冰島嘅洪永城，及陳瀅一齊上去麵店幫襯嘅Instagram限時動態，超蓮形容陳瀅同洪永城係女神同男神，真係畀足面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547646450_f49a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547646450_f49a.jpg&h=bee95874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547646450_0088.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547646450_0088.jpg&h=7a1b13c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547646450_1975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547646450_1975.jpg&h=033c3dcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79ffcb60a354e46be845255672bc32c8c646cc31","tid":984454,"uid":76314,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T21:21:11.000Z","msg":"猷君唔係生係二房同三房真係可惜"},{"pid":"f72849ff578e177b80ad862f51e36fee820cb95e","tid":984454,"uid":30708,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:13:52.000Z","msg":"有錢又靚仔<br />\n想食乜都得啦"},{"pid":"081d6f84ed9a0243ed553b940c40a7d73a5a7042","tid":984454,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:40:1